original_title: Coming Out: A Collection of Stories
overview: Hosted by State Senator Shiela Kuehl, 'Coming Out: A collection of Stories', is a in-debth investigation of what it means to be gay/lesbian and how each person has grown to come to grips with their sexuality. Coming Out is an elightening and freeing experience, and those who have experienced it share thier most intimate stories.
title: Coming Out: A Collection of Stories
